Jokes are difficult.

178
00:08:12,430 --> 00:08:15,040
我以前认识一个有自闭症的小孩  皮特
I used to know a kid with autism. Peter.

179
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:17,390
他有点奇怪  但是人非常好
He was kind of weird but super nice.

180
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,010
以前认识
Used to know?

181
00:08:20,570 --> 00:08:22,090
你现在不认识他了吗
You don't know him anymore?

182
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:23,170
他去世了
He died.

183
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,950
出了车祸
Hit by a car.

184
00:08:26,220 --> 00:08:27,680
你有朋友去世吗
You know anyone who died?

185
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,830
我的弟弟
My brother.

186
00:08:30,290 --> 00:08:31,490
真糟糕
That sucks.

187
00:08:35,070 --> 00:08:37,260
你为什么做那么多CT扫描
Why did you have the other CT scans?

188
00:08:37,260 --> 00:08:38,720
我的父母有...
My parents have...

189
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,680
你们把害怕生病称作什么
uh, what's the word for fear of getting sick?

190
